## Tor Hidden Service Configuration
## Kerosene Backend — v3 Onion Service

# Disable SOCKS proxy (we don't need outbound Tor circuits for routing)
SocksPort 0

# Hidden service: forward .onion port 80 → app container on port 8080
HiddenServiceDir /var/lib/tor/kerosene_service/
HiddenServiceVersion 3
HiddenServicePort 80 app:8080

# Logging
Log notice stdout

# Reduce footprint
DataDirectory /var/lib/tor
NumCPUs 1
